cluster:
is a combination of two or more nodes in which a adata stored and provide a search capability across all servers
Index:
Index is a collection of documents
Node:
A node is a single server that holds a data, this node can be in any cluster
Shards:
An index can be devidend into many shards, it's a subset of index and collection of documents


